        <span class="en">Mouse entry spawns 6 vertical aurora columns near the cursor X, with hues cycling over time (cyan→magenta→violet). Each column is a linear-gradient beam composited via <code>mix-blend-mode: screen</code>. Column positions oscillate sinusoidally, simulating the dancing curtains of a real aurora borealis.</span>
